quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  7,182,"As for those who reject Our signs, We will gradually lead them to destruction without them realizing it"
  7,183,"I will give them respite, but My plan is firm"
  7,184,"Have they not reflected that their fellow [Prophet] is not insane? He is none but a clear warner"
  7,185,"Have they not observed the dominions of the heavens and earth and all that Allah has created, and that the end of their term might be near? In what message after this [Qur’an] will they then believe"
  7,186,"Whoever Allah causes to stray, there is none to guide him; He will leave them to wander blindly in their transgression"
  7,187,"They ask you [O Prophet] about the Hour, “When will it come to pass?” Say, “Its knowledge is only with my Lord. None can reveal its due time except Him. It will be heavy on the heavens and earth; it will only come to you by surprise.” They ask you as if you are well-aware of it. Say, “Its knowledge is only with Allah, but most people do not know.”"
  7,188,"Say, “I have no power to benefit or harm myself, except what Allah wills. If I had knowledge of the unseen, I would have acquired much good, and no evil would have touched me. I am only a warner and bearer of glad tidings for people who believe.”"